      title: 'Keep Food Safe After a Disaster or Emergency | Food Safety | CDC #2 Steps to take during a power outage Keep refrige',
      summary: 'Steps to take during a power outage Keep refrigerator and freezer doors closed.',
      steps: [
        'If the doors stay closed, food will stay safe up to: 4 hours in a refrigerator, 48 hours in a full freezer, 24 hours in a half-full freezer.',
