      title: 'Wilderness Travel Basics - Olympic National Park (U.S. National Park Service) #2 The Ten Essentials Wildlife Clothing & Equipment',
      summary: 'The Ten Essentials Wildlife Clothing & Equipment Emergencies Map & Compass Climbing Snow Travel Off-trail Hiking River Crossings Cell Phones Winter Travel Weather Glaciers Plants S',
