      title: 'Wilderness Travel Basics - Olympic National Park (U.S. National Park Service) #8 A creek which you easily crossed in the morning,',
      summary: 'A creek which you easily crossed in the morning, or when you began your trip, may not be so easily crossed later that day or week.',
