        'However, it is important to learn the habits and behavioral patterns of classes of animals.',
        'For example, animals that are excellent choices for trapping, those that inhabit a particular range and occupy a den or nest, those that have somewhat fixed feeding areas, and those that have trails leading from one area to another.',
