      title: 'FM 21-76 Survival Manual #242 Page 157.',
      summary: 'Page 157.',
      steps: [
        '9-1 Chapter 9 Survival Use of Plants After having solved the problems of finding water, shelter, and animal food, you will have to consider the use of plants you can eat.',
