      title: 'FM 21-76 Survival Manual #646 Page 393.',
      summary: 'Page 393.',
      steps: [
        'FM 3-05.70 B-3 Acacia Acacia farnesiana Description: Acacia is a spreading, usually short tree with spines and alternate compound leaves.',
        'Its individual leaflets are small.',
        'Its flowers are ball-shaped, bright yellow, and very fragrant.',
        'Its bark is a whitish-gray color.',
      ],
