      title: 'FM 21-76 Survival Manual #653 Page 400.',
      summary: 'Page 400.',
      steps: [
        'FM 3-05.70 B-10 Bael fruit Aegle marmelos Description: This is a tree that grows from 2.4 to 4.6 meters (8 to 15 feet) tall, with a dense spiny growth.',
        'T he fruit is 5 to 10 centimeters (2 to 4 inches) in diameter, gray or yellowish, and full of seeds.',
        'Habitat and Distribution: Bael fruit is found in rain forests and semievergreen seasonal forests of the tropics.',
