        'Characteristics: As with all true vipers that liv e in the desert, it finds refuge by burrowing in the heat of the day, coming out at night to feed.',
        'It is difficult to detect when buried; therefore, many bites re sult from the snake being accidentally stepped on.',
        'Its venom is hemotoxic, caus ing severe damage to blood cells and tissue.',
      ],
