      summary: 'Page 653.',
      steps: [
        'FM 3-05.70 H-4 NATIONAL OCEANIC AND ATMOSPHERIC ADMINISTRATION Cumulonimbus clouds Cumulonimbus is the cloud formation resulting from a cumulus cloud building up, extending to great heights, and forming in the shape of an anvil.',
        'You can expect a thunderstorm if this cloud is moving in your direction.',
