      title: '热射病的快速降温动作',
      summary: '高热加意识改变要边呼救边强力降温。',
      steps: [
        'Heat exhaustion symptoms include heavy sweating, weakness, dizziness, headache, nausea or vomiting, muscle cramps, and pale, clammy skin.',
