      title: 'Thalassemias - Blood Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 The 2 main types are Alpha-thalassemia (the alph',
      summary: 'The 2 main types are Alpha-thalassemia (the alpha globin chain is affected) Beta-thalassemia (the beta globin chain is affected) Alpha-thalassemia is most common in people with Afr',
      steps: [
