      title: 'Precautions and Adverse Reactions During Blood Transfusion - Blood Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 After double-checking labels on the bags of bloo',
      summary: 'After double-checking labels on the bags of blood that are about to be given to ensure the units are intended for that recipient, the health care professional gives the blood to th',
