      title: 'Excessive Clotting - Blood Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Excessive Clotting (Thrombophilia) By Michael B.',
      summary: 'Excessive Clotting (Thrombophilia) By Michael B.',
      steps: [
        'Streiff , MD , Johns Hopkins University School of Medicine Reviewed/Revised Modified Jul 2025 v775245 Excessive clotting (thrombophilia) occurs when the blood clots too easily or excessively.',
        'Causes | Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Multimedia | Inherited and acquired disorders can increase blood clotting.',
