      summary: 'Secondary Iron Overload (Secondary Hemochromatosis) By James Peter Adam Hamilton , MD , Johns Hopkins University School of Medicine Reviewed/Revised Jan 2025 | Modified Apr 2025 v8',
      steps: [
        'Causes | Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | More Information | People often feel weak and tired.',
