      title: 'Macroglobulinemia - Blood Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Because this antibody is made by a single clone,',
      summary: 'Because this antibody is made by a single clone, it is called a monoclonal antibody and also is known as the M-protein.',
      steps: [
