      title: 'Platelet Dysfunction - Blood Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Platelet Dysfunction By David J.',
      summary: 'Platelet Dysfunction By David J.',
      steps: [
        'Kuter , MD, DPhil , Harvard Medical School Reviewed/Revised Modified May 2024 v7535213 Platelet dysfunction may be due to a problem in the platelets themselves or to an external factor that alters the function of normal platelets.',
        'Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Multimedia | (See also Overview of Platelet Disorders and Overview of Thrombocytopenia .) Platelets are cells that are made in the bone marrow and circulate in the bloodstream and help blood clot .',
