      id: 'merck-home-topic-0077-chunk-0002',
      title: 'Effects of Aging on the Musculoskeletal System - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 This change also limits the range of motion of j',
      summary: 'This change also limits the range of motion of joints.',
      steps: [
        'Loss of muscle (sarcopenia) is a process that starts around age 30 and progresses throughout life.',
        'In this process, the amount of muscle tissue and the number and size of muscle fibers gradually decrease.',
