      summary: 'Muscles By Alexandra Villa-Forte , MD, MPH , Cleveland Clinic Reviewed/Revised Jan 2025 | Modified Jul 2025 v728419 Multimedia | There are three types of muscles: Skeletal Smooth C',
      steps: [
        'Muscular System 3D Model Skeletal muscle is what most people think of as muscle, the type that can be contracted to move the various parts of the body.',
