      title: 'Infectious Arthritis - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Sometimes, arthritis develops in people who have',
      summary: 'Sometimes, arthritis develops in people who have infections that do not involve the bones or joints, such as infections of the genital organs or digestive organs.',
