      summary: 'Medical History and Physical Examination in Musculoskeletal Disorders By Alexandra Villa-Forte , MD, MPH , Cleveland Clinic Reviewed/Revised Feb 2024 | Modified Aug 2025 v11570852 ',
      steps: [
