      title: 'Medical History and Physical Examination in Musculoskeletal Disorders - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Medical History During a musculoskeletal evaluat',
      summary: 'Medical History During a musculoskeletal evaluation, doctors ask people about musculoskeletal symptoms but also look for other symptoms, such as fever, chills, weight loss, rash, e',
