      summary: 'Metatarsal Joint Pain By James C.',
      steps: [
        'Connors , DPM , Kent State University College of Podiatric Medicine Reviewed/Revised Modified Oct 2025 v26371258 Pain in the joints of the ball of the foot (metatarsophalangeal joints) may originate within the joints themselves.',
