      title: 'Plantar Fasciitis - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Other terms used to describe plantar fasciitis i',
      summary: 'Other terms used to describe plantar fasciitis include plantar fasciosis, calcaneal enthesopathy, and calcaneal spur syndrome ( heel spur ).',
      steps: [
        'A heel spur is a pointed growth of extra bone on the heel bone.',
        'It is caused over time by a combination of increased pull on the fascia and foot dysfunction.',
