      title: 'Sesamoiditis - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Sesamoiditis By James C.',
      summary: 'Sesamoiditis By James C.',
      steps: [
        'Connors , DPM , Kent State University College of Podiatric Medicine Reviewed/Revised Modified Oct 2025 v26371449 Sesamoiditis is pain around the 2 small bones (the sesamoid bones) below the metatarsal head where it adjoins the big toe (first metatarsal head).',
        'Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Multimedia | Symptoms include pain when walking (especially barefoot) or while wearing certain types of shoes.',
        'The diagnosis is based on an examination of the foot.',
        'Orthoses, offloading pads, and new shoes can help relieve pain.',
      ],
