      steps: [
        'Connors , DPM , Kent State University College of Podiatric Medicine Reviewed/Revised Oct 2025 | Modified Jan 2026 v103587815 Sever disease is inflammation of the growth plate of the heel bone (calcaneus) in children around the age of puberty.',
        'Treatment | Multimedia | (See also Overview of Bone Disorders in Children .) Sever disease is an osteochondrosis.',
