        'The accumulations of crystals cause flares (attacks) of painful inflammation in and around joints.',
        'Causes | Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Prognosis | Multimedia | Accumulations of uric acid crystals can intermittently cause severe joint or tissue pain and inflammation.',
