      summary: 'Herpetic Whitlow By David R.',
      steps: [
        'Steinberg , MD , Perelman School of Medicine at the University of Pennsylvania Reviewed/Revised Modified May 2024 v35322787 Herpetic whitlow is a viral infection of the fingertip.',
