      title: 'Kienböck Disease - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Kienböck Disease (Kienböck\'s Disease) By David R',
      summary: 'Kienböck Disease (Kienböck\'s Disease) By David R.',
      steps: [
        'Steinberg , MD , Perelman School of Medicine at the University of Pennsylvania Reviewed/Revised Modified May 2024 v35322852 Kienböck disease is the death of bone due to an impaired blood supply ( osteonecrosis ) affecting the lunate bone in the hand.',
        'Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Multimedia | (See also Overview of Hand Disorders .) The lunate bone is one of the carpals in the wrist.',
        'Bones in the Wrist The carpals are the bones in the wrist.',
        'They are located between the bones of the forearm and those of the hand.',
      ],
