      title: 'IgG4-Related Disease - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 IgG4-Related Disease (IgG4-RD) By Cory Perugino',
      summary: 'IgG4-Related Disease (IgG4-RD) By Cory Perugino , DO , Harvard Medical School Reviewed/Revised Modified Nov 2024 v50499116 Immunoglobulin G4-related disease (IgG4-RD) is an uncommo',
      steps: [
        'Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Prognosis | Symptoms depend on which organs are affected.',
        'Most people with IgG4-RD are middle-aged to older men, but the disorder can affect people of any age and sex.',
        'The exact cause of IgG4-RD is unknown, but it likely involves a problem with the immune system .',
        'IgG4-RD can damage organs before people notice symptoms and seek medical care.',
