      title: 'Osteoarthritis (OA) - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Before the age of 40, men develop osteoarthritis',
      summary: 'Before the age of 40, men develop osteoarthritis more often than do women, often because of injury or deformities.',
      steps: [
