  KnowledgeEntry(
      id: 'merck-home-topic-0130-chunk-0001',
      title: 'Overview of Spondyloarthritis - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Overview of Spondyloarthritis By Kinanah Yaseen',
      summary: 'Overview of Spondyloarthritis By Kinanah Yaseen , MD , Cleveland Clinic Reviewed/Revised Modified Apr 2024 v42285006 Spondyloarthritis (also called spondyloarthropathy or spondyloa',
      steps: [
        'For example, they may cause back pain, inflammation of the eye ( uveitis ), digestive symptoms, and rashes.',
        'Some are strongly associated with the HLA-B27 gene.',
        'Because they cause many of the same problems and share genetic characteristics, some experts think these disorders share similar causes and ways of causing symptoms.',
        'Spondyloarthritis causes joint inflammation, similar to rheumatoid arthritis .',
      ],
      contraindications: const <String>[],
