      title: 'Reactive Arthritis - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Reactive Arthritis By Kinanah Yaseen , MD , Clev',
      summary: 'Reactive Arthritis By Kinanah Yaseen , MD , Cleveland Clinic Reviewed/Revised Apr 2024 | Modified Mar 2026 v8551672 Reactive arthritis (previously called Reiter syndrome) is a spon',
      steps: [
        'Symptoms | Diagnosis | Treatment | Prognosis | More Information | Multimedia | Joint pain and inflammation can occur in response to an infection, usually of the genitourinary or gastrointestinal tract.',
