      title: 'Fibromyalgia - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Fibromyalgia (Myofascial Pain Syndrome; Fibrosit',
      summary: 'Fibromyalgia (Myofascial Pain Syndrome; Fibrositis; Fibromyositis) By Deepan S.',
      steps: [
        'Dalal , MD, MPH , Brown University Reviewed/Revised Modified Mar 2024 v38404776 Fibromyalgia is characterized by poor sleep, fatigue, mental cloudiness, and widespread aching and stiffness in soft tissues, including muscles, tendons, and ligaments.',
