      title: 'Difficulty Moving - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Joint disorders A joint may have limited range o',
      summary: 'Joint disorders A joint may have limited range of motion because of: Pain Previous joint injury causing significant scar tissue Prolonged joint immobilization (for example, when a ',
