      title: 'Joint Stiffness - Bone, Joint, and Muscle Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 For example, if stiffness lasts for less than 15',
      summary: 'For example, if stiffness lasts for less than 15 minutes, the joint is probably not inflamed.',
      steps: [
