      title: 'Effects of Aging on the Nervous System - Brain, Spinal Cord, and Nerve Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 HEALTHY LIVING Effects of Aging on the Nervous S',
      summary: 'HEALTHY LIVING Effects of Aging on the Nervous System By Mark Freedman , MD, MSc , University of Ottawa Reviewed/Revised Modified Apr 2025 v733604 Multimedia | Aging affects all pa',
