      title: 'Nerves - Brain, Spinal Cord, and Nerve Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #1 Nerves By Mark Freedman , MD, MSc , University o',
      summary: 'Nerves By Mark Freedman , MD, MSc , University of Ottawa Reviewed/Revised Modified Apr 2025 v733526 Multimedia | The peripheral nervous system consists of more than 100 billion ner',
      steps: [
        'Peripheral nerves consist of bundles of nerve fibers.',
        'These fibers are wrapped with many layers of tissue composed of a fatty substance called myelin.',
