      id: 'merck-home-topic-0182-chunk-0002',
      title: 'Overview of the Nervous System - Brain, Spinal Cord, and Nerve Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 Neurotransmitters trigger the receptors on the d',
      summary: 'Neurotransmitters trigger the receptors on the dendrites of the next nerve cell to produce a new electrical current.',
