      title: 'Brain Dysfunction by Location - Brain, Spinal Cord, and Nerve Disorders - MSD Manual Consumer Version #2 This characteristic is called left-hemisphere la',
      summary: 'This characteristic is called left-hemisphere language dominance.',
      steps: [
